@startuml
title Admin login - exact function calls

actor Admin
participant "AdminLoginPage" as LoginPage
participant "react-hook-form\nhandleSubmit()" as HandleSubmit
participant "onSubmit()" as OnSubmit
participant "useLoginMutation()" as UseLoginMutation
participant "loginAdmin()" as LoginAdminFacade
participant "loginAdminHttp()" as LoginAdminHttp
participant "buildApiUrl()" as BuildApiUrl
participant "Program.cs\nMapPost(/api/auth/login)" as LoginEndpoint
participant "AdminLoginRateLimiter.TryAcquire()" as LoginRateLimiter
participant "AdminSessionStore.CreateSession()" as CreateSession
participant "useNavigate()" as Navigate

Admin -> LoginPage : Submit username/password
LoginPage -> HandleSubmit : handleSubmit(onSubmit)
HandleSubmit -> OnSubmit : onSubmit(values)
OnSubmit -> UseLoginMutation : loginMutation.mutateAsync(values)
UseLoginMutation -> LoginAdminFacade : loginAdmin(username, password)
LoginAdminFacade -> LoginAdminHttp : loginAdminHttp(username, password)
LoginAdminHttp -> BuildApiUrl : buildApiUrl("/api/auth/login")
BuildApiUrl --> LoginAdminHttp : absolute URL
LoginAdminHttp -> LoginEndpoint : POST /api/auth/login
LoginEndpoint -> LoginRateLimiter : TryAcquire(HttpContext)
LoginRateLimiter --> LoginEndpoint : allowed
LoginEndpoint -> CreateSession : CreateSession(username)
CreateSession --> LoginEndpoint : session id + csrf token
LoginEndpoint --> LoginAdminHttp : 200 OK + Set-Cookie + AdminSessionResponse(csrfToken)
LoginAdminHttp --> LoginAdminFacade : AdminSession
LoginAdminFacade --> UseLoginMutation : session
UseLoginMutation -> UseLoginMutation : queryClient.setQueryData(authQueryKeys.session, session)
UseLoginMutation --> OnSubmit : resolve mutateAsync
OnSubmit -> Navigate : navigate(redirect)
Navigate --> Admin : browser navigates to /admin or redirect route

@enduml
